    "It is useful to understand the embedding (vectors) generated by DNNs.",
    "With t-SNE, we can understand the semantically related APIs and SE terms [152] calculated by deep learning.",
    "A heat map is usually used to visualize network parameters.",
    "By visualizing parameters of a layer, we can understand which part of information on which the network focuses more.",
    "A heat map assumes the more important (in deeper color) a region is, the more weight the network assigns to features in that area."
